Minister of Communications Nomvula Mokonyane, will brief media on the outcomes of the Cabinet meeting held on Wednesday 24 April 2018. Members of the media are invited to attend as follows: Date: Thursday, 25 April 2018Time:  10H00Venue:  Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Parliament, Cape Town NB: Journalists based in Pretoria are invited to participate via a video-link at Ronnie Mamoepa Media Centre, Tshedimosetso House, 1035 Francis Baard Street, Hatfield, Pretoria Follow us on Twitter: @GCISMedia @GovernmentZA #Post Cabinet Enquiries: Ms Phumla Williams Cell: 083 501 0139 Issued by Government Communication and Information System